{"id":"cli/config","title":"ng config","contents":"\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/config\", \"name\": \"config\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-config\">ng config<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/config#ng-config\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    <p>從本工作空間的 angular.json 檔案中獲取或設定 Angular 的配置值。</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">config</span> [<var>json-path</var>] [<var>value</var>]\n</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------mode_edit--code--------描述----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        描述\n    </h2>\n    <p>工作區在最上層有一個 CLI 配置檔案<code>angular.json</code>。<code>projects</code>物件包含工作區中每個專案的配置物件。</p>\n<p>你可以在程式碼編輯器中直接編輯配置，也可以用此命令在命令列上間接編輯。</p>\n<p>可配置的屬性名稱與命令選項名稱匹配，只是在配置檔案中，所有名稱都必須使用 camelCase，而在命令列選項上可以用 dash-case。</p>\n<p>有關更多詳細資訊，請參閱<a href=\"guide/workspace-config\">工作區配置</a>。</p>\n<p>有關 CLI 使用情況分析的配置，請參閱 <a href=\"cli/analytics\">ng analytics</a>。</p>\n\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">引數</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"width:15%\">引數</th>\n      <th style=\"width:40%\">說明</th>\n      <th>值型別</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">json-path</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>要設定或查詢的配置鍵，採用 JSON 路徑格式。例如：<code>a[3].foo.bar[2]</code>。如果沒有提供新值，則返回此鍵的當前值。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">value</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>如果提供，則為指定配置鍵的新值。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">選項</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th style=\"width:15%\">選項</th>\n    <th style=\"width:40%\">說明</th>\n    <th>值型別</th>\n    <th>預設值</th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--global</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>存取此呼叫者 home 目錄下的全域配置。</p>\n\n      <p><span class=\"cli-aliases\">別名:</span> -g</p>\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在控制檯顯示關於本命令的幫助資訊。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/workspace-config\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/analytics\n - cli/config#ng-config\n - guide/workspace-config\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/config/long-description.md\n-->"}